            Fighting South Korea's spy cam porn 'epidemic'
            Hidden cameras capture women undressing, going to the toilet, or even in changing rooms in South Korea. It's then uploaded to the internet without their knowledge.Soo-yuen Park has dedicated her life to helping women who have been victims of spy cam porn.BBC 100 Women names 100 influential and inspirational women around the world every year and shares their stories. Find us on Facebook, Instagram and Twitter and use #100Women.  
                
